snippet.title: Best VGM 644 - Dragon Quest III - Heavenly Flight
snippet.description:
Symphonic Suite version here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JBK7BZo2FQI

See also:
Best VGM 764 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rY3n4qQZTWY
Best VGM 1127 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZEUEQ4wlvi4
Best VGM 1542 - http://youtu.be/udNOf4W52hg
Best VGM 2300 - https://youtu.be/347m_waoqJ8

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES / SNES
Dragon Quest III (1996)
Heavenly Flight
Koichi Sugiyama
